data.title: FP Bhopal Edition 31 December 2023
data.meta_description:
FP Bhopal Edition 31 December 2023 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. - Prime Minister Narendra Modi inaugurated a renovated railway station and newly built airport in Ayodhya on Saturday. 
- He appealed to people to light special lamps called "Shri Ram Jyoti" in their homes on January 22nd to celebrate the consecration ceremony of the Ram temple.
- Modi said Lord Ram, who was once "living under a tent", will now be seated in a grand temple, ending a 500-year wait.
